  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Instead of internally depending on `web3.eth.contract`, we should instead depend on `@truffle/contract`. This would remove a great deal of our internal dependence on `web3.js`, and it would cause us to better define `@truffle/contract` for the needs of the Truffle project as a whole.\r\n\r\nCreating this as an (empty) epic, as it's likely that a fair amount of scoping work would need to be done before we can embark on this effort.\r\n\r\nNote: This was captured from an internal session where we discussed **potential** future breaking changes for major releases. Until the team assigns this ticket, this is merely a proposal, and not a commitment to make this specific change.",
